replies.body: Can be kind of toxic, but generally a deceny person. Fun to chat with and such. Used to client, but apparently doesn't anymore, which you have the character to do and is pretty respectable imo. replies.body:
Avicus is kind of like Badlion in the sense that you have to do specific things to be good as possible. 

Most important thing in pvp is aim, by FAR. Then strafing, straightlining is also optional, but imo takes more skill because you need to know how to keep reach and you need to get the combo, if you don't you have nothing. 
Sprint reset and it's just a lot of practice tbh. Ping matters, but there are ways to make the most of every level of ms.
